title: How to S or S+ (Bronze Style)

embed.description: Every game is a story; visit the new League of Legends match history to check out how this one ends and share your own!

body:
Hey guys it's Roxas24!!!!! bronze 3 rep. I wanted to get S on Ez for level 7 mastery. I put up a link on my last game which I thought was at least an S but I got an S- can anyone tell me what I did wrong? Thank youuuuu!

My summoner is Roxas24

replies.body:
Not enough CS
Not enough assists
Not enough overall dmg
You didn't buy many pink wards (control wards)
Not enough towers destroyed just by you

Tip: ask your team to last hit objectives so you have a higher chance to get an S. Baron last hit is very valuable.
